Author: fuckidy-007
Text: It’s fine, I’m fine. Everything is fine. One donut is FINE. I’m just going to start my fast early and try not to think about this..... fuck fuck fuck fuck fuck okay it’s fine I’m fine I’m fine I’m FINE ITS FINE EVERYTHING IS FINE

Author: BellaArcher
Text: If you're not into purging then please try to not go down that road. One donut is okay, please try to fight the ~urge to purge~
